Last Conversation helps you in fetching the details like phone number, dialled, missed and recieved calls along with the last message conversation you had with the contact. Once you start the application, you can enter the contact name which you wanted to search and select the auto suggested contact from the drop down list shown. If you want to do search by some characters which are not auto suggested, you can go ahead and click on the text field. This will carry the search with the given characters. Once the search is made you can see the list of contacts matching your search criteria. For all these contacts this application will show the last conversation details.

